AzurVeda VedaLibImageJPEG
Image Library extending VedaLib and VedaLibImage.
Please read the documentation in the headers.
author: victorien ferry & www.m4nkind.com, and the Independent JPEG Group.
 This library provide a JPEG Image class for AzurVeda contexts.
 It uses some part of the original jpeg-6b package (the jpg reading), and the error handling
 code was modified to forbid the use of setjmp(). As stated in the original 'Readme' file
 provided with jpeg-6b, this code can be re-used and even modified if it is clearly shown.
 The original README from jpeg-6b can be found in the Readme_libjpeg file.
